Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.77,0:00:20.39,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Akihisa Yoshii is a young man{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.39,0:00:23.90,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}who is very particular about everything he does.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.90,0:00:25.57,Main,,0,0,0,,Time to eat!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.07,0:00:31.24,Main,,0,0,0,,When I have salt water as a side\Ndish and sugar water as the main,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.24,0:00:33.37,Main,,0,0,0,,the meal seems a little extravagant, doesn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.37,0:00:36.58,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The degree to which he is particular{\i0}\N{\i1}about things gets lower every day.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.37,0:00:39.87,Main,,0,0,0,,Coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.21,0:00:46.88,Main,,0,0,0,,Long time no see, Aki.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.55,0:00:49.05,Main,,0,0,0,,S...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.05,0:00:50.38,Main,,0,0,0,,Sis...?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.60,0:01:00.81,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What grows on its own? Hmm, what is it?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.81,0:01:03.48,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}One more chance, one more{\i0}\N{\i1}chance. Never never give up!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.48,0:01:06.73,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}One more chance, one{\i0}\N{\i1}more chance. Never give up!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.73,0:01:15.41,Main,,0,0,0,,BAKA and TEST\N-Summon the Beasts-
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.78,0:01:19.25,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}"Nice to encounter you,"{\i0}\N{\i1}that one's too easy!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.25,0:01:22.00,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}There's only one answer{\i0}\N{\i1}that I decided on at the start{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.00,0:01:24.63,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}My heart fluttered. Will I pass?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.63,0:01:27.25,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I won't panic whether{\i0}\N{\i1}it's a matter of love or war{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.25,0:01:29.84,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I sigh as I cram all night long{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.84,0:01:32.47,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}There's a genius dreamer inside of me{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.47,0:01:35.14,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It'd be nice if everything I wanted came true{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.14,0:01:37.56,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Pay no mind to other people's worlds{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.56,0:01:40.14,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Perfect-area complete!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.14,0:01:42.81,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'll definitely be waiting right here.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.81,0:01:49.19,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Perfect-area, I can hear someone wishing for it{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.19,0:01:50.48,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Ah! Ear! Ear!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.48,0:01:53.78,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Why? We just keep missing each other{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.78,0:01:56.41,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}If you came to me for advice, it'd go like{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.41,0:01:59.03,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}"So, friends?" "Yes, friends."{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.03,0:02:00.95,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That's a sad 0 points.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.95,0:02:04.25,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}No! Do it again! Rewrite it!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.25,0:02:06.38,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1} I'm serious, one{\i0}\N{\i1}more chance please{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.38,0:02:11.63,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}You know, there's a future{\i0}\N{\i1}more wonderful than now{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.63,0:02:17.64,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Make it more wonderful than{\i0}\N{\i1}now... my life, my life, my life{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.56,0:02:24.23,MainTop,,0,0,0,,"Episode 9" "Kisses, Breasts, and Ponytails"\N{\i1}Akira Yoshii. 23 years old. E cup.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.23,0:02:28.02,MainTop,,0,0,0,,"Episode 9" "Kisses, Breasts, and Ponytails"\N{\i1}She is Akihisa's older sister who lives abroad.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.02,0:02:30.82,Main,,0,0,0,,Sis! You came here dressed like that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.82,0:02:35.20,Main,,0,0,0,,Why're you raising your voice\Nall of a sudden? That's absurd.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.20,0:02:37.28,Main,,0,0,0,,Says someone who walks\Naround in her bathrobe...!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.28,0:02:40.33,Main,,0,0,0,,You should let people finish their stories.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.33,0:02:42.91,Main,,0,0,0,,I have a reason for being dressed like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.91,0:02:45.87,Main,,0,0,0,,Sorry, Sis. What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.87,0:02:47.42,Main,,0,0,0,,"A Day in the Life of Akira, Story of an Elegant Day, Episode 1"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.42,0:02:54.01,Main,,0,0,0,,I walked quite a ways from the airport\Nin the heat with heavy luggage.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.01,0:02:54.88,Main,,0,0,0,,Uh-huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.88,0:03:00.01,Main,,0,0,0,,When I got on the train, I saw\Nmyself all sweaty in the window.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.01,0:03:01.26,Main,,0,0,0,,Uh-huh, uh-huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.26,0:03:03.14,Main,,0,0,0,,Although I was going to see my brother,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.14,0:03:05.81,Main,,0,0,0,,I should pay attention to my appearance.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.81,0:03:08.06,Main,,0,0,0,,I didn't want to show myself all sweaty.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.06,0:03:09.61,Main,,0,0,0,,Uh-huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.61,0:03:12.03,Main,,0,0,0,,So, in order to deal with the sweat,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.03,0:03:14.94,Main,,0,0,0,,I changed into a bathrobe\Nsince it's highly absorbent.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.94,0:03:16.53,Main,,0,0,0,,Stop right there! That's messed up!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.53,0:03:19.66,Main,,0,0,0,,Thus, I was able to reunite with\Nmy little brother while maintaining
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.66,0:03:23.29,Main,,0,0,0,,the dignified appearance\Nhis older sister should have.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.29,0:03:24.87,Main,,0,0,0,,And that's even more messed up!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.87,0:03:27.04,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm glad that the train was rather empty.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.04,0:03:27.79,Main,,0,0,0,,"A Day in the Life of Akira, Story of an Elegant Day, Episode 2"
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.79,0:03:30.84,Main,,0,0,0,,"A Day in the Life of Akira, Story of an Elegant Day, Episode 2"\NIf it was crowded, I would've had problems changing.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.84,0:03:32.63,Main,,0,0,0,,"A Day in the Life of Akira, Story of an Elegant Day, Episode 2"\NHold on a sec. Where'd you change?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.63,0:03:32.88,MainTop,,0,0,0,,"Omitted (024 - 1)"
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.25,0:03:34.51,MainTop,,0,0,0,,"Omitted (024 - 2)"
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.51,0:03:39.47,Main,,0,0,0,,Aki, I came here today because\NI have to attend to important affairs.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.47,0:03:40.64,Main,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.64,0:03:44.97,Main,,0,0,0,,I'll start my investigation\Nnow on how you're living
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.97,0:03:48.94,Main,,0,0,0,,and decide if it's okay to\Nlet you continue to live alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.94,0:03:50.23,Main,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.23,0:03:53.78,Main,,0,0,0,,When you started living alone,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.78,0:03:56.40,Main,,0,0,0,,I gave you two conditions to follow.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.40,0:03:58.74,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm sure you haven't forgotten them, have you?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.74,0:04:01.16,Main,,0,0,0,,If I say I did, will you get upset?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.16,0:04:03.08,Main,,0,0,0,,No, I won't.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.08,0:04:04.91,Main,,0,0,0,,Good! Well, I completely--
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.91,0:04:07.25,Main,,0,0,0,,Instead of getting upset, I'll give you a kiss.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.25,0:04:08.75,Main,,0,0,0,,...completely remember them!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.75,0:04:12.88,Main,,0,0,0,,Moreover, I'll give you an incredible kiss,\Nthen marriage will no longer be possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.88,0:04:15.21,Main,,0,0,0,,What're you planning to\Ndo to your own little brother?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.21,0:04:19.80,Main,,0,0,0,,Relax. It's me who won't be able to get married.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.80,0:04:21.51,Main,,0,0,0,,I can't relax!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.51,0:04:25.10,Main,,0,0,0,,You'll live the rest of your life\Nfeeling guilty towards your sister
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.10,0:04:27.81,Main,,0,0,0,,since she won't be able to get married.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.81,0:04:29.94,Main,,0,0,0,,I remember them well, so please spare me!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.94,0:04:31.90,Main,,0,0,0,,Then, tell me what they are.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.90,0:04:34.31,Main,,0,0,0,,Uhm...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.31,0:04:36.74,Main,,0,0,0,,Aki. Close your eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.74,0:04:39.40,Main,,0,0,0,,Ah! First, I can play video\Ngames for 30 minutes a day!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.40,0:04:42.32,Main,,0,0,0,,Second, illicit sexual\Nrelationships are forbidden!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.32,0:04:43.57,Main,,0,0,0,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.57,0:04:44.95,Main,,0,0,0,,Are they wrong?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.95,0:04:47.04,Main,,0,0,0,,When they're correct, I can't kiss you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.04,0:04:49.37,Main,,0,0,0,,Is that something you should be sorry about?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.12,0:04:53.08,Main,,0,0,0,,It's tidier than I thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.08,0:04:55.46,Main,,0,0,0,,You thought it'd be messier?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.46,0:04:58.42,Main,,0,0,0,,You're at that age, too, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.42,0:05:02.47,Main,,0,0,0,,I thought that your room would be\Nburied in two thousand dirty books.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.47,0:05:04.39,Main,,0,0,0,,I don't have money to buy two thousand of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.39,0:05:06.76,Main,,0,0,0,,In other words, you have at least one book?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.76,0:05:07.77,Main,,0,0,0,,Ah!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.77,0:05:11.52,Main,,0,0,0,,As a semi-illicit sexual\Nrelationship, that's minus 20 points.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.52,0:05:13.06,Main,,0,0,0,,What's that score?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.06,0:05:18.23,Main,,0,0,0,,It's an assessment used to determine\Nif it's okay for you to continue living alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.23,0:05:21.90,Main,,0,0,0,,I'll compare it with your next periodical\Ntest and reconsider the approval.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.90,0:05:24.91,Main,,0,0,0,,In other words, that means that if\NI get 20 more points in the next midterm,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.91,0:05:28.45,Main,,0,0,0,,it'll cancel out that 20 points, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.45,0:05:30.50,Main,,0,0,0,,Let me ask you, just in case...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.50,0:05:33.17,Main,,0,0,0,,You're not in any other illicit\Nsexual relationships, are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.17,0:05:35.50,Main,,0,0,0,,Doing what gives me how many negative points?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.50,0:05:38.59,Main,,0,0,0,,If you hold hands with a\Ngirl, that's minus 100 points.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.59,0:05:39.84,Main,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.84,0:05:44.09,Main,,0,0,0,,If you go out with girls to\Nsee movies or have crepes,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.09,0:05:50.18,Main,,0,0,0,,or if girls make you lunch or waffles,\Nyou'll get minus 50,000 points.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.18,0:05:51.48,Main,,0,0,0,,What's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.48,0:05:53.64,Main,,0,0,0,,No, nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.64,0:05:56.11,Main,,0,0,0,,You're a healthy young man.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.11,0:05:59.53,Main,,0,0,0,,I understand very well that you don't\Nknow what to do with your young body.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.53,0:06:01.57,Main,,0,0,0,,I didn't say that.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.57,0:06:04.70,Main,,0,0,0,,So I'll concede as much as I can as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.70,0:06:07.20,Main,,0,0,0,,Although I forbid illicit\Nsexual relationships with girls...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.20,0:06:11.08,Main,,0,0,0,,I think I can accept your illicit\Nsexual relationships with guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.08,0:06:12.16,Main,,0,0,0,,What happened?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.16,0:06:16.71,Main,,0,0,0,,What happened to your sense\Nof values while living abroad?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.75,0:06:20.30,Main,,0,0,0,,The stars look... pretty.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.30,0:06:24.47,Main,,0,0,0,,These scores are...\Nmore terrible than I expected.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.47,0:06:27.18,Main,,0,0,0,,Be that as it may, I tried hard in my own way.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.18,0:06:30.47,Main,,0,0,0,,Trying hard is only a means to an end.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.47,0:06:33.56,Main,,0,0,0,,No matter how invaluable\Nthe act of trying hard is,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.56,0:06:37.65,Main,,0,0,0,,if you become proud of the effort itself,\Nyou're mistaking the means for the end.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.65,0:06:39.61,Main,,0,0,0,,You don't have to say that.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.61,0:06:41.32,Main,,0,0,0,,If you don't want me to say that to you,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.32,0:06:44.49,Main,,0,0,0,,please overcome the subjects\Nyou're bad at. Even one subject is fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.49,0:06:48.16,Main,,0,0,0,,Tsk. You do have a subject\Nyou're bad at too, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.16,0:06:49.53,Main,,0,0,0,,What is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.53,0:06:50.49,Main,,0,0,0,,Cooking.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.49,0:06:53.12,Main,,0,0,0,,That has nothing to do with academics.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.12,0:06:55.46,Main,,0,0,0,,But it's necessary for living.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.46,0:07:00.00,Main,,0,0,0,,--Well, all you're good at is academics. As for the rest...\N--If you say more, I'll kiss you to shut you up.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.00,0:07:02.30,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, I was wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.80,0:07:05.93,Main,,0,0,0,,Yuuji... I want you to show me your cell.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.93,0:07:07.34,Main,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.34,0:07:09.97,Main,,0,0,0,,They said on a TV show\Nlast night that the traces
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.97,0:07:12.85,Main,,0,0,0,,of your partner's infidelity can be\Nfound on their cell. Show it to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.85,0:07:15.60,Main,,0,0,0,,I refuse.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.60,0:07:17.81,Main,,0,0,0,,My eyes... My eyes hurt like they're burning!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.81,0:07:20.98,Main,,0,0,0,,If you resist, I'll take it by force.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.98,0:07:23.32,Main,,0,0,0,,Hey! Don't take my pants, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.32,0:07:26.49,Main,,0,0,0,,I heard that guys like\Nseeing a shirt on a naked body.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.49,0:07:28.45,Main,,0,0,0,,It's not that we like to\Nsee {\i1}ourselves {\i0}like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.45,0:07:29.74,Main,,0,0,0,,I wanna see it, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.74,0:07:33.62,Main,,0,0,0,,Ah! Okay! I'll give it\Nto you! I'll give it to you!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.62,0:07:34.37,Main,,0,0,0,,You will...?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.37,0:07:36.87,Main,,0,0,0,,Don't be so openly disappointed!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.87,0:07:39.88,Main,,0,0,0,,Geez... Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.88,0:07:42.80,Main,,0,0,0,,You get more e-mail from Yoshii than me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.80,0:07:44.25,Main,,0,0,0,,So what?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.25,0:07:46.84,Main,,0,0,0,,That means that you're\Nhaving a love affair with Yoshii.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.84,0:07:48.84,Main,,0,0,0,,Are you kidding me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.64,0:07:52.68,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Can I stay overnight at your place?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.68,0:07:55.48,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I kinda don't want to... go home tonight.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.35,0:07:58.73,Main,,0,0,0,,Hey, wait... Shouko! Sto--!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.73,0:08:00.56,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm all set now.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.56,0:08:01.94,Main,,0,0,0,,Good morning, Akihisa.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.94,0:08:02.44,Main,,0,0,0,,Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.44,0:08:06.53,Main,,0,0,0,,What happened, Akihisa?\NYou look healthier than usual.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.53,0:08:09.49,Main,,0,0,0,,Yeah. I had a decent\Nbreakfast this morning, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.49,0:08:12.32,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Akihisa sold his manga books and{\i0}\N{\i1}video games to a second-hand shop{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.32,0:08:15.12,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}and got money for food.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.12,0:08:19.83,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Even if it's just during Sis's stay,{\i0}\N{\i1}I'd better pretend that I live a healthy life.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.83,0:08:22.38,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Or I'll get negative points.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.55,0:08:26.76,Main,,0,0,0,,Cool Biz?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.76,0:08:29.38,Main,,0,0,0,,Who'd follow Cool Biz just below their waist?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.38,0:08:31.34,Main,,0,0,0,,This is all because you sent me a weird e-mail!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.34,0:08:33.05,Main,,0,0,0,,There was nothing weird about it, was there?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.05,0:08:35.47,Main,,0,0,0,,Then read it out loud.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.47,0:08:36.89,MainTop,,0,0,0,,"Sent Box" "001 Yuuji" Let me stay over" "002 Yuuji: Love"\N"003 Yuuji: Don't let go" "004 Yuuji: Together"
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.60,0:08:42.86,Main,,0,0,0,,"Can I stay overnight at your place?\NI kinda don't want to... go home tonight."
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.86,0:08:45.11,Main,,0,0,0,,I don't get your true feelings!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.11,0:08:47.94,Main,,0,0,0,,You should wait to do something\Nlike that until you are older!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.94,0:08:50.07,Main,,0,0,0,,That's obscene, Yoshii!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.00,0:08:58.50,Main,,0,0,0,,Baka Test
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.37,0:09:04.88,Main,,0,0,0,,Uhm... Yoshii.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.88,0:09:06.71,Main,,0,0,0,,Go to the nurse's office.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.71,0:09:09.80,Main,,0,0,0,,You think something's wrong if I'm studying?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.93,0:09:15.47,Main,,0,0,0,,Did something happen, Aki?\NTo see you suddenly studying...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.47,0:09:16.14,Main,,0,0,0,,Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.14,0:09:18.43,Main,,0,0,0,,You're acting strange today.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.43,0:09:21.27,Main,,0,0,0,,Nothing... really.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.73,0:09:26.11,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh? You've got quite a well-made lunch today.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.11,0:09:28.03,Main,,0,0,0,,Yeah, for a change...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.03,0:09:30.74,Main,,0,0,0,,Amazing... Who made it?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.74,0:09:31.45,Main,,0,0,0,,Me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.45,0:09:32.36,Main,,0,0,0,,Liar.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.36,0:09:33.53,Main,,0,0,0,,That's a lie.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.53,0:09:34.91,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm not lying!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.91,0:09:38.70,Main,,0,0,0,,This is by someone very skilled.\NIs it either Sakamoto or Tsuchiya?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.70,0:09:40.33,Main,,0,0,0,,Be honest and spit it out.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.33,0:09:42.62,Main,,0,0,0,,Who made it for you?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.62,0:09:45.96,Main,,0,0,0,,I'll leave it to your imagination now.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.96,0:09:49.30,Main,,0,0,0,,You don't wanna go home today, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.30,0:09:51.76,Main,,0,0,0,,You're that dirty, Aki?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.76,0:09:53.43,Main,,0,0,0,,I don't want to believe it!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.43,0:09:54.97,Main,,0,0,0,,I hate you, Yoshii!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.97,0:09:58.26,Main,,0,0,0,,What were you imagining?!\NAnd hey, why is Kubo here too?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.26,0:09:59.97,Main,,0,0,0,,By the way, Akihisa...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.97,0:10:02.10,Main,,0,0,0,,why do you wanna stay over at my place?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.10,0:10:05.31,Main,,0,0,0,,--What? I-It's because I suddenly realized studying is important.\N--Don't lie.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.31,0:10:06.02,Main,,0,0,0,,Hey, I didn't even finish!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.02,0:10:09.98,Main,,0,0,0,,Well, midterms are coming up soon.\NThe idea of a study group isn't too bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.98,0:10:10.53,Main,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.53,0:10:13.32,Main,,0,0,0,,But... at your place.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.32,0:10:18.41,Main,,0,0,0,,N-N-N-No! Not my place! Today isn't... good!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.41,0:10:20.25,Main,,0,0,0,,What're you hiding?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.25,0:10:21.79,Main,,0,0,0,,Shall we go check it out?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.79,0:10:23.87,Main,,0,0,0,,A house search...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.87,0:10:26.54,Main,,0,0,0,,In any case, today isn't\Ngood! It's really messy!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.54,0:10:28.79,Main,,0,0,0,,I'll help you tidy up.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.79,0:10:30.00,Main,,0,0,0,,Well... but...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.00,0:10:33.13,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Oh yeah, if the mess is from something{\i0}\N{\i1}that girls don't like to touch, then...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.13,0:10:36.14,Main,,0,0,0,,I've got two thousand dirty\Nbooks scattered all over, so...!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.93,0:10:38.85,Main,,0,0,0,,I'll tidy them up!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.85,0:10:40.10,Main,,0,0,0,,I'll ditch them all!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.10,0:10:41.85,Main,,0,0,0,,Leave it to us!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.85,0:10:45.56,Main,,0,0,0,,Dammit! That backfired big time!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.11,0:10:50.61,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Idiot Test{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.70,0:10:56.11,Main,,0,0,0,,Are you really coming to my place?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.11,0:10:58.53,Main,,0,0,0,,What on earth are you hiding, Akihisa?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.53,0:11:01.24,Main,,0,0,0,,Considering that you brought\Na lunch that someone made...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.24,0:11:04.00,Main,,0,0,0,,In all probability, it's a girlfriend.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.00,0:11:06.79,Main,,0,0,0,,What's that mean, Aki?! Explain it!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.79,0:11:08.88,Main,,0,0,0,,Uhm, I didn't say anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.88,0:11:15.01,Main,,0,0,0,,Don't worry. There's no way that Yoshii\Nwould date someone behind our back.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.01,0:11:18.14,Main,,0,0,0,,Isn't that right, Yoshii?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.14,0:11:20.51,Main,,0,0,0,,Your eyes are serious.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.68,0:11:25.10,Main,,0,0,0,,Well, once we go inside,\Nit'll probably be all clear.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.10,0:11:27.60,Main,,0,0,0,,Unlock the door, Akihisa.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.60,0:11:29.65,Main,,0,0,0,,I... I don't want to!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.65,0:11:32.94,Main,,0,0,0,,Do you wanna experience the\Nagony of wearing nothing but a shirt?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.94,0:11:35.49,Main,,0,0,0,,I'd appreciate it if you\Nlook upward with watery eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.49,0:11:38.37,Main,,0,0,0,,Are you gonna sell it? Are\Nyou gonna sell my pure heart?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.37,0:11:43.41,Main,,0,0,0,,Tsuchiya, have him unhook\Nthe top two buttons of his shirt.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.41,0:11:45.62,Main,,0,0,0,,Himeji, your request is too detailed!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.62,0:11:48.12,Main,,0,0,0,,Okay, okay! I'll open it!\NYou'll be happy if I open it, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.12,0:11:49.13,Main,,0,0,0,,Your buttons?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.13,0:11:50.09,Main,,0,0,0,,No, the door!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.09,0:11:51.50,Main,,0,0,0,,Ahhhhh!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.50,0:11:54.13,Main,,0,0,0,,There's already something that\NI can't come up with an excuse for!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.13,0:11:56.51,Main,,0,0,0,,This physical evidence is\Nabout as good as it gets.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.51,0:11:59.39,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm so jealous that I wanna kill him.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.39,0:12:01.64,Main,,0,0,0,,This isn't good, Yoshii.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.64,0:12:02.10,Main,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.10,0:12:07.73,Main,,0,0,0,,The size of this bra... doesn't fit you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.73,0:12:09.48,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}She's not gonna admit it.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.56,0:12:12.44,Main,,0,0,0,,Ah! Th-That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.44,0:12:14.48,Main,,0,0,0,,That's a cotton puff for makeup.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.48,0:12:16.99,Main,,0,0,0,,No, that's a fish cake.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.99,0:12:19.03,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}A fish cake?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.36,0:12:20.62,Main,,0,0,0,,Ah! This is...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.62,0:12:22.03,Main,,0,0,0,,Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.03,0:12:25.58,Main,,0,0,0,,A healthy lunch for a woman...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.58,0:12:27.83,Main,,0,0,0,,What's the matter, Himeji?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.83,0:12:29.75,Main,,0,0,0,,I can't keep on denying any more.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.75,0:12:34.21,Main,,0,0,0,,Why are underwear and\Ncosmetics okay but a lunch isn't?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.21,0:12:36.30,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh, you brought friends?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.30,0:12:38.63,Main,,0,0,0,,Ah! An older pretty woman...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.63,0:12:40.13,Main,,0,0,0,,A nice body with big breasts...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.13,0:12:41.93,Main,,0,0,0,,You're cruel, Yoshii!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.93,0:12:44.01,Main,,0,0,0,,Give me back my pure heart!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.01,0:12:47.77,Main,,0,0,0,,I don't understand what\Nyou're saying anymore...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.77,0:12:51.06,Main,,0,0,0,,Okay. I'll be honest and tell you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.06,0:12:52.61,Main,,0,0,0,,She's my older sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.61,0:12:54.32,Main,,0,0,0,,Older sister?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.32,0:12:56.99,Main,,0,0,0,,My name is Akira Yoshii.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.99,0:13:03.83,Main,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much, everyone, for\Nbeing friends with my stupid brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.83,0:13:06.16,Main,,0,0,0,,I hope you'll continue to be friends with him.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.16,0:13:09.29,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}This is surprising! She looks like{\i0}\N{\i1}an ordinary older sister in every way.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.29,0:13:10.96,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Thanks, Sis!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.75,0:13:13.96,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm Yuuji Sakamoto.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.96,0:13:15.54,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm Kouta Tsuchiya.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.54,0:13:18.09,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm Hideyoshi Kinoshita.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.09,0:13:21.09,Main,,0,0,0,,People often make a mistake,\Nbut I'm not a girl. I'm...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.09,0:13:23.43,Main,,0,0,0,,A boy, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.43,0:13:26.97,Main,,0,0,0,,You're the only one who\Nrecognized me as a guy at a glance!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.97,0:13:31.14,Main,,0,0,0,,Sure, since there's no way that\Nmy stupid, ugly, good-for-nothing
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.14,0:13:34.65,Main,,0,0,0,,little brother can get female friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.65,0:13:37.73,Main,,0,0,0,,So these two are boys as well, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.73,0:13:41.61,Main,,0,0,0,,What's with the sudden rude\Nremarks?! You were acting so nicely.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.61,0:13:43.45,Main,,0,0,0,,These three are all girls, okay?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.45,0:13:45.83,Main,,0,0,0,,No, she's right about me being a guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.83,0:13:47.33,Main,,0,0,0,,Girls?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.62,0:13:53.12,Main,,0,0,0,,Since when have you started bringing girls home?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.12,0:13:53.58,Main,,0,0,0,,Ugh!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.58,0:13:54.00,Main,,0,0,0,,"Akihisa's\Nallotted points"
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.00,0:13:57.80,Main,,0,0,0,,You'll get minus 200 points for the act\Nof illicit sexual relationships with girls!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.80,0:14:00.63,Main,,0,0,0,,Nooooo!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.63,0:14:04.26,Main,,0,0,0,,Akihisa... You've been\Nhaving hardships too, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.26,0:14:05.68,Main,,0,0,0,,Yuuji...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.68,0:14:09.14,Main,,0,0,0,,I'll allow illicit sexual\Nrelationships with boys.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.14,0:14:10.73,Main,,0,0,0,,It's not like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.73,0:14:13.56,Main,,0,0,0,,I'll give you 10 points for that.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.56,0:14:16.27,Main,,0,0,0,,That doesn't make me happy or anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.27,0:14:19.19,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh, Akihisa, since we suddenly came uninvited,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.19,0:14:21.32,Main,,0,0,0,,we'll at least help you make dinner.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.32,0:14:22.99,Main,,0,0,0,,Okay. Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.99,0:14:23.82,Main,,0,0,0,,Me, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.82,0:14:26.87,Main,,0,0,0,,I'll help, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.87,0:14:29.08,Main,,0,0,0,,We'll be fine by ourselves!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.08,0:14:30.83,Main,,0,0,0,,You girls take it easy here.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.83,0:14:32.91,Main,,0,0,0,,What? But...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.91,0:14:34.50,Main,,0,0,0,,Sis, keep them company.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.50,0:14:37.54,Main,,0,0,0,,Okay. If you like, I can show you photo albums.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.54,0:14:38.84,Main,,0,0,0,,What? Is that okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.84,0:14:40.71,Main,,0,0,0,,Well then, I'll show you embarrassing pictures.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.71,0:14:42.01,Main,,0,0,0,,Anything but those!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.01,0:14:43.76,Main,,0,0,0,,That was a narrow escape.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.30,0:14:47.30,Main,,0,0,0,,So, what's on the menu?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.30,0:14:53.14,Main,,0,0,0,,With these, we can make {\i1}paella{\i0}. I like {\i1}paella{\i0}.
