Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.15,0:15:01.36,Main,,0,0,0,,No way. Since she doesn't know how\Nto cook, she bought too much by mistake.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.95,0:15:07.16,Main,,0,0,0,,--Yeah, put it over there.\N--This one is really good, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.16,0:15:08.66,Main,,0,0,0,,Here you go.
