Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.63,0:15:24.63,Main,,0,0,0,,These are pictures of Aki taking\Na bath when he was seven years old.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.63,0:15:27.05,Main,,0,0,0,,So this was when he was\Nin elementary school, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.05,0:15:30.26,Main,,0,0,0,,These are pictures of Aki taking\Na bath when he was ten years old.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.26,0:15:33.39,Main,,0,0,0,,Hold on a sec! Why are they\Nall pictures of me taking a bath?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.39,0:15:36.73,Main,,0,0,0,,These are pictures of Aki taking a\Nbath when he was thirteen years old.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.65,0:15:40.90,Main,,0,0,0,,Hey... Why are you all suddenly quiet?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.90,0:15:43.99,Main,,0,0,0,,And these are pictures of\NAki taking a bath yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.99,0:15:46.03,Main,,0,0,0,,When'd you take them?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.03,0:15:48.45,Main,,0,0,0,,--Don't look at them! Don't look!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.45,0:15:48.95,Main,,0,0,0,,--Hey, don't leave the pot unattended.\N--Don't look at them! Don't look!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.95,0:15:51.28,Main,,0,0,0,,--Hey, don't leave the pot unattended.\N--Don't look at my private parts!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.28,0:15:54.04,Main,,0,0,0,,Noooooooo!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.54,0:15:56.21,Main,,0,0,0,,They made delicious-looking food.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.21,0:15:58.67,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh? You made {\i1}paella{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.67,0:16:01.96,Main,,0,0,0,,Huh? Didn't you buy those foods for that?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.96,0:16:04.67,Main,,0,0,0,,Th-That looks good, Aki.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.67,0:16:09.55,Main,,0,0,0,,S-So you really can cook, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.55,0:16:16.98,Main,,0,0,0,,--Ahhh! You must've seen them! You all must've seen them!\N--Seriously, Aki is restless. Negative 10 points.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.98,0:16:19.56,Main,,0,0,0,,It's your fault, Sis!\NYou keep trying to annoy me!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.56,0:16:21.65,Main,,0,0,0,,You hate me, don't you, Sis?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.65,0:16:25.24,Main,,0,0,0,,No. I do like you, Aki...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.24,0:16:26.90,Main,,0,0,0,,What?
