Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.57,0:16:30.49,Main,,0,0,0,,This is terrible!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.49,0:16:33.24,Main,,0,0,0,,There's a Japanese saying that goes like this:
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.24,0:16:35.70,Main,,0,0,0,,"The stupider the child is,\Nthe more darling he is."
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.70,0:16:40.42,Main,,0,0,0,,Give up, Akihisa. She loves you\Nmore than anyone in the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.42,0:16:43.88,Main,,0,0,0,,Does that mean that she thinks\NI'm the stupidest in the world?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.88,0:16:47.55,Main,,0,0,0,,I think you're the stupidest in the world, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.55,0:16:52.14,Main,,0,0,0,,I, too, am convinced that there's no\None else who's stupider than you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.14,0:16:57.52,Main,,0,0,0,,--Stop it! Don't hurt my glass heart, everyone!\N--You really are stupid, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.06,0:17:02.98,Main,,0,0,0,,Well... now that we're full,\Nshall we start studying?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.98,0:17:06.48,Main,,0,0,0,,If you like, I can help you study.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.48,0:17:07.82,Main,,0,0,0,,Is that okay?
