Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.55,0:17:30.01,Main,,0,0,0,,I found six of them under the bed.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.01,0:17:32.68,Main,,0,0,0,,My top secret!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.68,0:17:35.43,Main,,0,0,0,,Aki, I'll give you minus 60 points for this.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.43,0:17:37.60,Main,,0,0,0,,Does that mean 10 negative points per book?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.60,0:17:40.64,Main,,0,0,0,,No. That's because you didn't have\Nbooks with a focus on older sisters.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.64,0:17:43.06,Main,,0,0,0,,That's too unfair!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.06,0:17:46.23,Main,,0,0,0,,Well then, please use them as\NHealth and Physical Education references.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.23,0:17:49.15,Main,,0,0,0,,Stop it. My hobby is gonna\Nbe exposed to the light of day!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.15,0:17:52.65,Main,,0,0,0,,Looks like Aki tends to study by focusing
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.65,0:17:57.33,Main,,0,0,0,,on the topic of girls with\Nbig breasts and a ponytail.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.33,0:18:00.00,Main,,0,0,0,,Ah!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.00,0:18:03.12,Main,,0,0,0,,W-Well, let's start studying, shall we?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.12,0:18:05.79,Main,,0,0,0,,Why are you tying your hair up, Mizuki?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.79,0:18:08.51,Main,,0,0,0,,I thought it'd be in the\Nway while I'm studying, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.51,0:18:10.96,Main,,0,0,0,,I'll do it for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.96,0:18:13.34,Main,,0,0,0,,You're mean, Minami!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.34,0:18:16.89,Main,,0,0,0,,Why? That way, it won't be\Nin the way while studying, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.89,0:18:18.77,Main,,0,0,0,,Aki, you get minus 100 points.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.77,0:18:19.93,Main,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.93,0:18:21.39,Main,,0,0,0,,Why?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.39,0:18:24.81,Main,,0,0,0,,Learn the reason on\Nyour own in your future life.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.19,0:18:30.65,Main,,0,0,0,,What's the matter, Muttsulini?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.65,0:18:33.15,Main,,0,0,0,,Where are the other 1,994 books?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.15,0:18:35.62,Main,,0,0,0,,So you took it seriously...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.95,0:18:39.87,Main,,0,0,0,,--G-Good morning, Yoshii.\N--Good morning, Aki.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.87,0:18:41.41,Main,,0,0,0,,Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.41,0:18:43.12,Main,,0,0,0,,Good morning, you two.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.12,0:18:44.87,Main,,0,0,0,,You changed your hairstyle, Himeji?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.87,0:18:48.71,Main,,0,0,0,,Y-Yes, to change my mood.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.71,0:18:50.92,Main,,0,0,0,,You changed your breast style, Minami?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.92,0:18:53.47,Main,,0,0,0,,No! They were bigger when I woke up!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.47,0:18:54.59,Main,,0,0,0,,Are you serious?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.59,0:18:58.60,Main,,0,0,0,,Since I'm still growing,\Nsomething like this can happen!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.31,0:19:02.93,Main,,0,0,0,,I won't allow you to profane\Nsecondary sex characteristics.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.93,0:19:04.60,Main,,0,0,0,,Tsk.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.23,0:19:08.31,Main,,0,0,0,,Yesterday was fun, wasn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.31,0:19:10.19,Main,,0,0,0,,We made progress in our studies, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.19,0:19:12.94,Main,,0,0,0,,But it looks like I'll be\Nforbidden to live alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.94,0:19:15.15,Main,,0,0,0,,I wish Sis would go back to America.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.15,0:19:17.70,Main,,0,0,0,,You shouldn't talk about your family like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.70,0:19:19.70,Main,,0,0,0,,She's a nice sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.70,0:19:23.79,Main,,0,0,0,,She isn't nice. She tries to kiss\Nme and gives me negative points.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.79,0:19:26.04,Main,,0,0,0,,She enjoys teasing me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.04,0:19:28.42,Main,,0,0,0,,That's not true.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.42,0:19:31.42,Main,,0,0,0,,Your sister loves you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.42,0:19:34.55,Main,,0,0,0,,Does that mean she really thinks I'm stupid?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.55,0:19:40.31,Main,,0,0,0,,She watches you and your surroundings very well.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.51,0:19:46.56,Main,,0,0,0,,I think that means she really cares about you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.90,0:19:52.48,Main,,0,0,0,,I wonder if that's how it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.48,0:19:55.40,Main,,0,0,0,,What shall I make tonight?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.40,0:20:00.87,Main,,0,0,0,,She came all the way back to Japan.\NMaybe Japanese dishes would be good.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.08,0:20:03.91,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm home!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.91,0:20:06.79,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh, welcome home, Aki.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.79,0:20:09.17,Main,,0,0,0,,Well then, I'll go get food for dinner, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.17,0:20:12.80,Main,,0,0,0,,Dinner? Wait, Aki.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.80,0:20:14.17,Main,,0,0,0,,What is it, Sis?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.17,0:20:16.38,Main,,0,0,0,,Your midterms are coming up soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.38,0:20:20.22,Main,,0,0,0,,Can you afford to spare\Nyour time for cooking right now?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.22,0:20:23.85,Main,,0,0,0,,I can't, but... you came all the way back, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.85,0:20:26.56,Main,,0,0,0,,You're mistaking the means for the end.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.56,0:20:27.27,Main,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.27,0:20:30.98,Main,,0,0,0,,I came to check on your life, Aki.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.98,0:20:35.03,Main,,0,0,0,,What's the point in you using your time for me?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.03,0:20:38.90,Main,,0,0,0,,I won't know what to do if you use it as\Nan excuse when the results aren't good.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.90,0:20:42.28,Main,,0,0,0,,You don't have to cook for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.28,0:20:45.83,Main,,0,0,0,,You focus on studying. I'll cook fo--
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.83,0:20:48.21,Main,,0,0,0,,What's with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.21,0:20:51.79,Main,,0,0,0,,All you care about is the test results, right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.79,0:20:55.05,Main,,0,0,0,,I'll go study as you wish!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.43,0:21:06.39,Main,,0,0,0,,Stupid Sis!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.39,0:21:09.69,Main,,0,0,0,,I'll definitely get good\Nscores and show her I can do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.32,0:21:16.44,Main,,0,0,0,,Good morning, Yoshii.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.44,0:21:17.74,Main,,0,0,0,,Good morning, Aki.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.74,0:21:19.95,Main,,0,0,0,,D-Don't talk to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.95,0:21:22.70,Main,,0,0,0,,The stuff I memorized and\Ncrammed into my head might come out.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.70,0:21:24.03,Main,,0,0,0,,R-Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.03,0:21:27.12,Main,,0,0,0,,Then, we'll leave you alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.12,0:21:31.67,Main,,0,0,0,,Okay then, we'll start the test. Start now!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.79,0:21:34.88,Main,,0,0,0,,"Q. Answer the following questions."
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.88,0:21:35.80,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I can do this!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.80,0:21:41.13,MainTop,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Question 1. 334 BC! The last king of{\i0}\N{\i1}the Achaemenid Empire of Persia was{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.13,0:21:43.39,MainTop,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Alexander the Great! Next!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.47,0:21:47.39,MainTop,,0,0,0,,He must be taking the test right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.39,0:21:50.06,MainTop,,0,0,0,,Well then, I guess I'll start, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.02,0:21:56.07,MainTop,,0,0,0,,{\i1}All right. I did my best.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.07,0:21:58.57,MainTop,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'll have another look at{\i0}\N{\i1}them in the remaining time.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.57,0:22:02.70,Main,,0,0,0,,Okay. Put your pencils down.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.70,0:22:05.20,Main,,0,0,0,,Those in the back, collect the answer sheets.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.20,0:22:06.66,Main,,0,0,0,,Ah!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.66,0:22:11.00,Main,,0,0,0,,"Name: Alexander the Great"
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.96,0:22:17.09,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Goodbye, my life of living alone.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.26,0:22:23.63,Main,,0,0,0,,Geez, you stupid Alexander the Great...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.63,0:22:26.47,Main,,0,0,0,,You put the first answer in\Nwhere you needed to put your name,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.47,0:22:28.81,Main,,0,0,0,,so the rest of the answers\Nbecame off by one, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.81,0:22:31.64,Main,,0,0,0,,Please...! Call me by my real name.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.64,0:22:33.39,Main,,0,0,0,,Darius III.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.39,0:22:36.65,Main,,0,0,0,,Ahh! Don't humiliate me any more than you have!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.65,0:22:40.90,Main,,0,0,0,,I could've gotten a decent\Nscore if I didn't blunder.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.90,0:22:43.32,Main,,0,0,0,,Do you think you'll be forgiven\Nif you make the same mistake
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.32,0:22:46.70,Main,,0,0,0,,in a real college entrance exam?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.70,0:22:48.49,Main,,0,0,0,,I tried very hard in my own way.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.49,0:22:53.91,Main,,0,0,0,,I thought I told you that trying\Nhard is only a means to an end.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.91,0:22:55.58,Main,,0,0,0,,Yes ma'am.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.75,0:23:02.76,Main,,0,0,0,,Sis is ruthless.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.23,0:23:16.40,Main,,0,0,0,,Geez... What a mess.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.40,0:23:19.77,Main,,0,0,0,,Hey, she doesn't cook, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.19,0:23:22.53,Main,,0,0,0,,"Half-cooked" "Forgot to put in saffron"\N"The heat was too high"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.53,0:23:23.86,Main,,0,0,0,,"Detergent got mixed in"\N"Sticky" "Too much salt"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.86,0:23:24.11,Main,,0,0,0,,"Terrible taste"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.11,0:23:27.91,Main,,0,0,0,,"Terrible taste"\NAre these... failed attempts at {\i1}paella{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.62,0:23:36.12,Main,,0,0,0,,Could it be that... she wanted to\Nmake my favorite food so she practiced?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.58,0:23:40.71,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Trying hard is only a means to an end.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.71,0:23:45.38,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}If you become proud of the effort itself,{\i0}\N{\i1}you're mistaking the means for the end.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.76,0:23:50.64,Main,,0,0,0,,Really... she's such a dummy.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.95,0:24:19.13,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'd have to say the first kiss{\i0}\N{\i1}tastes like strawberry milk{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.13,0:24:26.51,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}As it turns to evening,{\i0}\N{\i1}I'm pushing my bike home{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:26.51,0:24:33.77,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}So which is it, a delusion,{\i0}\N{\i1}a simulation, or a dream?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:33.77,0:24:41.06,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}After stumbling seven times,{\i0}\N{\i1}I stumble an eighth time, wahahaha{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:41.06,0:24:48.32,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Each day is different and{\i0}\N{\i1}every day is an anniversary{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:48.32,0:24:55.58,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Let's connect them together to that sky{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:55.58,0:25:02.88,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}My future is bright. Do I see{\i0}\N{\i1}myself becoming someone big?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:02.88,0:25:14.64,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Tomorrow too, for sure...{\i0}\N{\i1}it'll be sunny, with occasional smiles{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:30.49,0:25:31.87,Main,,0,0,0,,Say, Sis...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:31.87,0:25:32.66,Main,,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:32.66,0:25:36.99,Main,,0,0,0,,Thanks for everything. I like you a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:36.99,0:25:38.12,Main,,0,0,0,,What're you...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:38.12,0:25:40.12,Main,,0,0,0,,Of course, as family.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:40.12,0:25:43.67,Main,,0,0,0,,Even if you say such a nice thing,\NI won't overlook the test score.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:43.67,0:25:45.84,Main,,0,0,0,,That's a shame.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:45.84,0:25:46.84,Main,,0,0,0,,One of these days...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:46.84,0:25:47.80,Main,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:47.80,0:25:49.76,Main,,0,0,0,,One of these days, if I feel like it,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:49.76,0:25:52.43,Main,,0,0,0,,maybe I'll make dinner for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:52.43,0:25:53.85,Main,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:53.85,0:25:56.43,Main,,0,0,0,,That is only if I feel like it.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:56.43,0:25:58.27,Main,,0,0,0,,I look forward to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:59.48,0:26:00.48,Main,,0,0,0,,Sis...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:00.48,0:26:01.98,Main,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:01.98,0:26:04.94,Main,,0,0,0,,Do you know what the best spice is?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:04.94,0:26:07.36,Main,,0,0,0,,The best spice?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:07.36,0:26:13.07,Main,,0,0,0,,Since I don't cook, I don't know. What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:13.07,0:26:14.74,Main,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I wonder what it is!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:16.12,0:26:18.58,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Question 10. Name the Japanese novelist{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:26:18.58,0:26:20.95,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}who introduced the "Adolescent Detective Gang"{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:26:20.95,0:26:23.29,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}and the "Mystery Man of{\i0}\N{\i1}Twenty Faces" to the world.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:26:23.29,0:26:24.58,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The thief is among us!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:26:24.58,0:26:25.88,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's not me.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:26:25.88,0:26:27.96,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Next Episode! "Prep Tests,{\i0}\N{\i1}Mysterious Thieves, and Love Letters."{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:26:27.96,0:26:30.05,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}This will be on the test.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:26:30.05,0:26:35.05,MainTop,,0,0,0,,"Please join us again next week!"\N"Illustration: Mako Aboshi"
